#: ../../faq/v4_upgrade.rst:83
msgid ""
"The ``dsmr_mqtt`` process has been renamed to ``dsmr_client`` to support "
"more generic continuous data flows in the future (such as InfluxDB) and "
"to offload some blocking mechanics in ``dsmr_backend`` as well."
msgstr ""
"Het ``dsmr_mqtt`` proces is hernoemd naar ``dsmr_client`` om in de "
"toekomst wat meer generieke dataflows te ondersteunen (zoals InfluxDB), "
"maar ook om ``dsmr_backend`` wat meer te ontlasten."

